doctor.name: Prof. Dr. Anisa Begum
doctor.info: Prof. Dr. Anisa Begum is a Gynecologist in Rangpur. Her qualification is MBBS, FCPS (OBGYN), MCPS (OBGYN). She is working as a Gynecology, Obstetrics, Infertility Specialist & Surgeon doctor in Rangpur Medical College & Hospital. She regularly provides treatment to her patients at Doctor's Diagnostic Centre Unit-2, Rangpur. Practicing hour of Prof. Dr. Anisa Begum at Doctor's Diagnostic Centre Unit-2, Rangpur is 2.30pm to 9pm (Closed: Friday).
